<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-16622] Validator component fails with java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: protocol = https host = null</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-16622</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Same issue as reported in&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-14372&quot; title=&quot;Validator component fails with java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: protocol = http host = null&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CAMEL-14372&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CAMEL-14372&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. but for the https&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When the protocol is https, the url is corrupted and the host is lost.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
